dagger
Annotation Type Provides

@Documented
@Target(value=METHOD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Provides

Annotates methods of a module to create a provider method binding. The method's return type is bound to it's returned value. The object graph will pass dependencies to the method as parameters.

Author:
Bob Lee
